data.description:
Welcome to the stunning gem at 3716 Cobbleridge Drive in Charlotte, NC, offering a perfect blend of modern conveniences and comfortable living. This move-in-ready, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home features a freshly painted interior, and a cozy covered patio for entertaining and relaxation.
Nestled in a warm and welcoming neighborhood, you'll be just minutes away from the thriving University City area, providing you with an array of greenways, parks, shopping centers, and dining options. Spend your weekends immersed in nature at the serene Ribbon Walk Nature Preserve or enjoy outdoor activities at Reedy Creek Park. Discover unique shops and flavorful cuisine in University Place, then head over to PNC Music Pavilion for fantastic entertainment.
Don't miss out on this delightful property! Schedule a viewing today.
